John- A very good article but we need to go the next step and enlist
Gates, the JCS and others to identify systems and programs that are no
longer necessary and push for real cuts in those budgets. I remember a
speech Ben Cohen gave at my son Michael's High School graduation. He
said, "It's like shampoo, I look in the mirror and realize I don't need
that much anymore." A

